data.description: Welcome Home!  Only available due to relocation.   A great location in the Heritage Park community of Woodbury within close proximity to the pool, playground & clubhouse. With an open and bright floor plan, a beautiful kitchen and adjoining deck with vaulted ceilings.  There is an enjoyable fireplace to relax in front of at anytime. Beautiful private master suite that includes a nice tub to soak in.  Built-in office on the top floor nook to get work done. Finally, a finished lower level with a 3rd bedroom, 3/4 bath, and a walk-out to concrete patio for relaxing.
